      "date": "2012-12-22 22:59:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8a7e1666-4c86-11e2-875d-52540035b04c).  Ran 26 tests.  7 tests failed: sanity-quota, replay-ost-single, recovery-small, conf-sanity, replay-single, sanityn, sanity.",
