      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2138f8ae-5a89-11e2-84d3-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
