      "date": "2013-01-30 17:50:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nSeems like failure in replay-single is a known issue, and the situation with sanity-quota I've described in my comment for #change,4993:\n\nFailures in sanity-quota look strange. I've tried to run sanity-quota on stock lustre-master and it has failed the same way as with my patch. Then I checked the last few test requests on review.whamcloud.com and they showed that sanity-quota was not run at all.",
